# --- Documentation policy ---------------------------------------------------
# Only user-facing docs are tracked: README, usage guides, API/user references,
# and changelogs. Agent-generated planning artifacts (plans, specs, findings,
# audits, walkthroughs) stay local and are added only after an explicit
# document review.
